    "We performed 1500 classifications (500 inferences for each digit: 0, 1, and 2) to ensure statistical reliability.",
    "The representative classification results presented in Fig. 5f demonstrate accurate classification for all digits.",
    "Figure 5g shows the statistical outcomes of the 1500 classifications tasks, all of which reveal a classification accuracy of 100%.",
